<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-22 00:26 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1886 &Cx1f; tth-z
r s BC-BBA-THIEL-COLUMN-SPI &LR;      05-22 0876
