<HEADLINE>
WITH TEXAS BOXERS 
CHAMP CAMP WAS BOOT CAMP FOR FORT WORTH BOXERS
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By RICHIE WHITT 
c.2000 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
 
 
 
 
<TEXT>
