<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-22 02:53 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1968 &Cx1f; tab-z
r k BC-NISSAN-`MR.FIXIT'-ECO     05-22 1640
</HEADER>
<BODY>
