about 2 million people in the United States. It develops when the
regurgitation of stomach contents stimulates changes in the lining
of the esophagus -- the tube that carries food from the mouth to
the stomach -- so that it resembles the lining of the intestines.
(600 words. Slugged THROAT-CANCER-MED)
</P>
<P>
   -----
</P>
