</P>
<P>
   ``Providence,'' 1976.
</P>
<P>
   ``Arthur,'' 1980
</P>
<P>
   ``Chariots of Fire,'' 1980.
</P>
<P>
   ``Prospero's Books,'' 1992.
</P>
<P>
   ``Elizabeth,'' 1998.
</P>
<P>
   Theater
</P>
