<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-22 16:29 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2497 &Cx1f; ttx-z
r l BC-DRLAURA-1100(2Takes)-     05-22 0928
