relating to human rights.''
</P>
<P>
   _ the Canadian Broadcast Standards Council on Schlessinger's
anti-gay remarks
</P>
<P>
   _
</P>
<P>
   ``She just can't get the hang of being a TV host. She's having a
hard time walking with the microphone and talking at the same time,
and just looks awkward on camera. The worst part is, she won't
listen to anybody's advice.''
</P>
<P>
   _ an anonymous insider commenting on rehearsals for Dr. Laura's
