   GENERAL-SEX-CHARGE (Washington) _ More details emerging about
the investigation of charges of sexual misconduct made by a female
general against another general. By Steven Lee Myers.
</P>
<P>
   EPA-CADMIUM (Washington) _ The Environmental Protection Agency
is scouring the country for fertilizer and animal feed made from
imported raw materials contaminated with cadmium, a toxic metal.
(675 words)
