</P>
<P>
   &UR; ``On days that are like most days in my life so far _ days
when &LR; 
 &UR; I don't settle the conflict in Kosovo, win the lottery or &LR; 
 &UR; establish a system of economic and social opportunity that &LR; 
 &UR; creates true equality for all _ I'm willing to settle for the &LR; 
 &UR; very real joy that there is to be had in finding the perfect &LR; 
 &UR; kitten-heel pump.'' &LR;
