<P>
   _ Statement of purpose from  &UR; Kim France &LR; , editor in chief of
Lucky, a new magazine that bridges the gap between InStyle (which
in itself was People-Lite) and any mail-order catalog. Lucky
provides a meager sprinkling of text to anchor pages of pictures,
prices and ordering information on hundreds of products, and comes
with stickers to serve as markers for goods the reader wishes to
order.
</P>
