<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-22 20:30 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2752 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r e BC-M:I-2-FEATURE-LADN &LR;      05-22 1540
